value: Breeds from extreme northeastern Siberia across arctic North America to southwestern Baffin Island, south to the mouth of the Yukon, Hudson Bay (Severn River), and northern Labrador. Winters from the Gulf and southern Atlantic coasts of the United States through Central America and the West Indies to South America (coast of Peru on the west and southern BrazU, rarely farther, on the east).
